To edit the raw HTML markup, click the **Code view** toggle in the toolbar. Formatting support in code view is limited to the options available in the editor toolbar. Any additional CSS added through code view must be managed by you.

:::(Info) (<p class="fa-regular fa-circle-exclamation" data-type="icon"></p> NOTE)
Each editor block has a character limit of [X] characters. Custom content added to endpoint pages is retained when you regenerate or resync your API documentation.
:::
